[SN]TITLE[SN]
Pensioner's car targeted by vandal

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
An Angus pensioner's car has been badly damaged after a corrosive liquid was poured over it.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The woman's vehicle was targeted in Carnoustie's Burnside Street between 18:00 on Thursday and 11:30 on Friday.
A Police Scotland spokeswoman said the vehicle sustained "extensive damage" in the incident.
She said: "This has had a significant impact on the owner of the car, who is a 70-year-old lady who relied on her car to get around."
